{
  "stem": "6989.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 27.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think I cared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I remembered saying-- like she would say, you have to, you know, be quiet, or something like that, or hide.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I would say, so if it happens, it happens.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think I had that attitude.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remembered one time saying that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it was later on though when-- you know, during the war itself when the Russians were coming in.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's like I didn't care, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How did the family respond to the German occupation?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think that there were Germans around that farm.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See, later on-- I don't know how long I was there, but I was there sort of the longest-- months, several months.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know if it was four, or six, or someplace around there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After that-- and I don't know the reason for it-- she had another sister that lived in a city called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was married, that sister, and lived in the city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There we-- for some reason, we went to her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know the reason for it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "See, like the first reason, I knew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The second reason, I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But all I know is that we went to live with Anya.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Her name was Anya.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there I have to be hidden because her husband was a banderovets, which means like the equivalent of the SS but Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was sort of like an apartment, I think.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very small.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember it being very small.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember there was a bed in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at night, I used to sleep with her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "During the day, I was hidden also like in a little cellar.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
